  <title>XA27 Depends on an Amino-Terminal Signal-Anchor-Like Sequence to Localize to the Apoplast for Resistance to Xanthomonas oryzae pv oryzae</title>
  <URL>https://cn.bing.com/academic/profile?id=1c8c5f9c24558428b2e60e8ca08738ca&amp;encoded=0&amp;v=paper_preview&amp;mkt=zh-cn</URL>
